---
title: Pulled BBQ Chicken Breast Buns with Smoky Paprika Chips and Zesty Slaw
description: These Pulled BBQ Chicken Breast Buns are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R201_W02_UK_F4605-10_MB_MODULAR_high-743a7433.jpg
